title: ninja_duelist
---
Duelist: Quiet. The Leader is meditating, which means anyone who slams a door dies. Don't slam the door. ...You walked in without slamming. Fine. Acceptable. State your business.
-> Heard you're working with pirates now.
    <<jump ninja_duelist__1>>
-> Any tips for the bird?
    <<jump ninja_duelist__2>>
-> Carry on.
    The duelist resumes a kata that consists mostly of stepping on a single tile in five slightly different ways.
===

title: ninja_duelist__1
---
Duelist: Working WITH them. Not joining. There's a distinction. A pirate has never washed his hands in his life, and a ninja is mostly hands. The arithmetic is ugly. But the bird is uglier. After the bird's down, we go back to being insulted by their cologne and their volume.
-> Ask another question.
    <<jump ninja_duelist__0>>
-> Carry on.
    The duelist nods once. The nod is also a kata.
===

title: ninja_duelist__2
---
Duelist: It mimics. Don't believe a sound it makes — your own voice in your own kata could come out of its beak. Strike on the silence between its calls. If you hear yourself, you're already losing.
-> Ask another question.
    <<jump ninja_duelist__0>>
-> Carry on.
    The duelist nods once. The nod is also a kata.
===

title: ninja_leader
---
Shadow Oni: Stranger. You walked through our doorway without my permission, which means either you are very rude or very good. The Mockingbird stole a song that wasn't theirs to sing. We will end them. Even if it means standing shoulder to shoulder with a pirate.
-> Why team up with the pirates?
    <<jump ninja_leader__1>>
-> What's your grievance with the bird?
    <<jump ninja_leader__2>>
-> Where does the dojo stand on the cove?
    <<jump ninja_leader__3>>
-> Open the arena door.
    The Leader inclines her horned mask. Somewhere in the rafters, a paper lantern unrolls a sigil that wasn't there a moment ago. The far door slides aside.
===

title: ninja_leader__1
---
Shadow Oni: We are knives in the dark; the pirates are shouts in broad daylight. We don't share a worldview — we share a target. The bird mocks our katas as fluently as it mocks their shanties. A loud enemy and a quiet enemy still bury the same corpse.
-> Ask another question.
    <<jump ninja_leader__0>>
-> Open the arena door.
    The Leader's blade rests an inch out of its saya. The dojo holds its breath in the way only a room of disciplined breathers can.
===

title: ninja_leader__2
---
Shadow Oni: It learned a kata. ONE of ours. Not perfectly — but the bird performed it back at us in a courtyard at dawn, with our own footwork, and laughed. A bird does not laugh. A bird that does is no longer a bird; it is an insult that flies.
-> Ask another question.
    <<jump ninja_leader__0>>
-> Open the arena door.
    The Leader's blade rests an inch out of its saya. The dojo holds its breath in the way only a room of disciplined breathers can.
===

title: ninja_leader__3
---
Shadow Oni: Tell the Admiral the dojo will hold position on the eastern thermals. We will not steal his songs and he will not steal our shadows. The bird falls. After that, we go back to politely loathing each other from a distance.
-> Ask another question.
    <<jump ninja_leader__0>>
-> Open the arena door.
    The Leader's blade rests an inch out of its saya. The dojo holds its breath in the way only a room of disciplined breathers can.
===
